ISLAMABAD, Aug 13 (APP): Prime Minister Muhammad Shehbaz Sharif on Tuesday reiterated the resolve for a prosperous Pakistan through pursuance of reforms and continuous hard work.
On social media platform X, the prime minister, in Urdu language, posted that on the eve of Independence Day 2024, ‘it is their unwavering resolve for the progress and prosperity of Pakistan-“Reforms and continuous struggle”, “We will embellish Pakistan’s future”.
